*Improvements Made for Consistency*

Issue 1: The assistant sometimes asked unrelated follow-up questions.
Fix: Added rules to always base follow-ups on previous responses.

Issue 2: Tone shifted between formal and casual.
Fix: Strict instruction: “Maintain a polite and formal tone.”

Issue 3: Assistant answered its own questions.
Fix: Added constraint: “Never answer your own questions.”

Issue 4: Interview ended abruptly.
Fix: Added final evaluation step.
